					<h1 class="entry-title">Episode-1065- Mark Kirkwood on Hybrid Earthships and Building Community</h1>

					<div class="entry-meta">
						<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/kirkwood-on-hybrid-earthships-and-building-community" title="10:55 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">February 6, 2013</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/kirkwood-on-hybrid-earthships-and-building-community#comments" title="Comment on Episode-1065- Mark Kirkwood on Hybrid Earthships and Building Community">83 Comments</a></span>
											</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

