		<div class="comment-body"><p>The mix changes by use.<br />
Insulationn mix<br />
80% granulated styrafoam<br />
20% type I/II Portland<br />
And a large amount of fiber</p>
<p>Structural mix<br />
50% styrafoam<br />
50% Portland type I/II<br />
And a large amount of fiber.</p>
<p>Fiber can be pulped paper, shredded plastic, besalt  fiber, fiber glass fiber and so on.</p>
