		<div class="comment-body"><p>Also, on the poison PVC issue, there is a newish product out which is touted as being the un-PVC. It&#8217;s called Blu-Loc, or something like that, and apparently is doesn&#8217;t contain the evils of the polyvynilchloride compound.<br />
I haven&#8217;t yet used it in my own work, but other professionals I&#8217;ve talked to seemed happy with it.<br />
If you can find a specific irrigation supply store, they may have it, or know where it can be sourced.<br />
All the best,<br />
Sampson</p>
</div>

